high_descs: Walk straight to the small circle table with the lamp.
Pick up a watch from the table.
Turn around and walk towards the small black coffee table to your left.
Place the watch on the table.
Turn left, walk the sofa, turn left to the wall, and turn right to the the small black table with the lamp.
Pick up the other watch on the table.
Turn around and walk towards the small black coffee table to your left.
Place the watch next to the other watch on the table.
anns.task_desc: Transfer the two watches from the small circle table onto the coffee table.

high_descs: Go forward to the right side of the black end table with the lamp on top.
Pick up the wrist watch nearer to the edge on the left.
Turn left and go to the black coffee table on the left.
Place the wrist watch on the table near the edge in front of the golden statue.
Turn left and go back to the end table with the lamp on top.
Pick up the remaining wrist watch from the table.
Turn around and go back to the coffee table.
Place the wrist watch on the table on the left side of the first watch.
anns.task_desc: Put two wrist watches on the coffee table.
